{"tid":969482,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮顧問:中美初步談判樂觀","createTime":"2019-01-05T06:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T06:18:37.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae18b23a5ad35fcca9e060f60b6250f53b1e7ba1","tid":969482,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"中美下周舉行經貿問題副部級磋商，白宮經濟顧問庫德洛(Larry Kudlow)對外電表示，美國將在下周談判中要求中國減少補貼，並稱初步談判比往常更樂觀，但總是會有不確定性。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，下周在中國的貿易談判將討論知識產權盜竊問題，認為知識產權盜竊可能會對蘋果公司產生影響。<br />\n另外，庫德洛又說，美國經濟正在增長，就業增長巨大，而視線所及看不到經濟衰退。"},{"pid":"9d0d79f7909708b08ef9c902c82b14890deb02ea","tid":969482,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"停火 龍5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571669d54cf0d5fbdd5f12ce4dcb132346a338f4","tid":969482,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"全部都係大陸傾向既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bd08bbdfaee3ef954baf2bb33c1232f5781f01","tid":969482,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571669d54cf0d5fbdd5f12ce4dcb132346a338f4","tid":969482,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"全部都係大陸傾向既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"支文傳媒開盡馬力散播fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}